		"inclusion": "To add the device to the Z-Wave network:\r\n1.      Keep the device in Z-Wave range.\r\n2.      Power the device.\r\n3.      Set the main controller in (Security/non-Security Mode) add mode\r\n          (see the controller’s manual).\r\n4.      Quickly, three times press the Config Button, LED color will change \r\n          from Red to Blue.\r\n5.      Wait for the adding process to end.\r\n6.      Successful adding will be confirmed by the Z-Wave controller’s\r\n          Message and LED Colour will change to Green.",
