		"reset": "Reset procedure allows restoring the device back to its factory settings, which means all information about the Z-Wave controller will be deleted.\r\n\r\n1.      Press and Hold Config Button for 10 sec until White LED Indication \r\n          to start blinking.\r\n2.      Release Config button. Now you have 5sec to Reset Device \r\n          otherwise it back to Normal Mode.\r\n3.      Single Click Config Button.\r\n4.      After a few seconds, the device will be restarted, which is signaled\r\n          with the red LED indicator color.\r\n\r\nNOTE:- Please use this procedure only when the network primary controller is missing or otherwise inoperable."
